<h1>Susan DeRagon Joins AsiaInspection to Further Strengthen Consumer Product Testing Expertise</h1>

<p><i>Ms. DeRagon’s technical expertise contributes to enhanced program management for AI testing labs.</i></p>

<img src="https://s3.asiainspection.com/images/news/Sue.jpg" style="max-width:100%; float:right; margin:0px 0px 15px 15px;">

<p><b>Hong Kong – September 8, 2017</b></p>
<p>AsiaInspection (AI), a global quality control and supplier compliance service provider, announces that Susan DeRagon has joined their team to support AI’s technical teams and clients. Susan has over three decades of experience in the consumer products industry, with a focus on Toys and Children’s Products. In her previous role at UL, Susan provided technical, sales and consultative support globally, and participated in numerous committees and industry conferences. Joining AI’s lab in Buffalo, New York, Susan will leverage her extensive knowledge and experience to ensure that AI continues to provide its clients with the best quality of testing services and technical consulting.</p>
<p>Susan joins AI as a Senior Technical Consultant to further strengthen AI’s quality assurance offerings, which currently support the product compliance needs of major consumer goods brands and retailers. Susan’s contribution to the AI team will directly benefit the company’s clients through enhanced technical support and compliance program management.</p>
<p>“I am thrilled to start in my role with AI, and face the exciting challenges that come with it,” said Susan DeRagon. “I look forward to working with the world-class professionals that make up AI’s testing team. Together, we can help global brands and retailers ensure quality, safety and compliance for their products, and peace of mind for their consumers.”</p>
<p>Welcoming Susan to the AI team, Karolyn Helda, Managing Director said, “With over 32 years of technical knowledge and consumer industry experience, Susan is a highly valuable addition to the AI family. I’m confident she will play a key role in keeping AI at the top of the field for lab testing services. Last but not least, we look forward to having Susan represent AI as a respected speaker at professional and industry events. Welcome to the team!”</p>
<br />
<h2 style="font-size:18px;">About AI</h2>
<p><a href="http://www.asiainspection.com/" target="_blank">AsiaInspection (AI)</a> is a leading quality control and supplier compliance service provider that partners with brands, retailers and importers globally to secure and optimize their supply chain. AI performs Supplier Audit Programs, Product Inspections and Lab Testing in 85 countries.</p>
<p>With its unique online and mobile management platform for quality control, AI guarantees to be onsite within 48 hours of booking, compiling a detailed report available online the same day as the inspection. Headquartered in Hong Kong, AI has 20 offices, 4 in-house labs, and over 2,100 employees.</p>

